      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311808
    m_Localized: Now you know how to free dwarves. Find 10 now!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311809
    m_Localized: Antura is at the top of Sky Tower!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311810
    m_Localized: "Ten dwarves are locked in magic cages in Wroc\u0142aw."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311811
    m_Localized: Find the School Dwarf here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311812
    m_Localized: How can I help?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311813
    m_Localized: Find the key. Then open the cage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311814
    m_Localized: Move the plant to find it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311815
    m_Localized: Look at the star on the map.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311816
    m_Localized: "Free all 10 of my dwarf friends in Wroc\u0142aw."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311817
    m_Localized: First go to the Cathedral. They will help you read the map.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311818
    m_Localized: Long ago, I made Dwarf Tunnels in the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311819
    m_Localized: Now they have turned into magical vehicles.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311820
    m_Localized: We are at Bema Stop, near the Cathedral.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311821
    m_Localized: It has tall towers and bright windows.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311822
    m_Localized: Find the cathedral key and free the Bishop Dwarf.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311823
    m_Localized: The Bishop Dwarf is safe now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311824
    m_Localized: Use it to go to the City Center or Centennial Hall.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311825
    m_Localized: Answer this question to open the cage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311826
    m_Localized: Look at Market Square, the Town Hall, and Panorama Raclawicka.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311827
    m_Localized: They have tiny hats and tiny boots.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311828
    m_Localized: A key is under a flowerpot in the market.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311829
    m_Localized: Panorama Raclawicka is part of the Center hub.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311830
    m_Localized: It is a giant picture all around you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311831
    m_Localized: Find the Painter Dwarf here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311832
    m_Localized: This is the Painter Dwarf from the Center hub.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311833
    m_Localized: This dwarf loves colors, paint, and big pictures.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311834
    m_Localized: Find the key, then match the picture pieces to open the cage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311835
    m_Localized: The finished picture shows a key under the frame.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311836
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311837
    m_Localized: The Center area is done.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311838
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311839
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311840
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311841
    m_Localized: Welcome to the Centennial area.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311842
    m_Localized: Find the zoo key. Then talk to the zoo keeper.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311843
    m_Localized: There is a key behind the sign.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311844
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311845
    m_Localized: Another dwarf is near Centennial Hall.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311846
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311847
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311848
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311849
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311850
    m_Localized: The finished picture shows a key under the frame.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311851
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73338445496311852
    m_Localized: The fountain is the last place here.
